The paper deals with the problem of multi-view registration, which is a common task in computer vision and graphics. The use of Gaussian mixture models and the EM algorithm suggests that the paper may belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of rigid transformations and the focus on accuracy and efficiency suggest that the paper may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO), multimedia (cs.MM), or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
